Interface Component

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchitecturalElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComponentImpl

    public interface Component
extends ArchitecturalElement
    A representation of the model object 'Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Tenant
    • Type
    • Parameters
    • State
    • Required Interfaces
    • Provided Interfaces
    • Name
